Good family/animal movies to watch with your kids. My daughter likes it.  We watches movies together all the time.  This one has good movies.
THE COLLECTION OF MOVIES ARE NICE . I'VE SEEN 5 OF THEM BUT IT'S NICE TO HAVE THEM AT MY FINGER-TIP TO SEE AGAIN. DVDS ARE IN GREAT CONDITION. THANK YOU FOR THE PRICE.

I purchased these DVDs to entertain my children on a long car drive, thinking, "As long as they haven't seen it, they'll be happy."  What I learned is that my children actually have some taste, and were not entertained by the C quality of these movies.
Many different adventures involving dogs.  These are great to get together with the family and watch.  I highly recommend these movies.  Well done!!!!!
This is definitely for all the dog-lovers out there.  All are adorable and lovable.  Hard to pick a favorite, you just have to watch them all.  Great for Family night!

All these movies are good family entertainment.  I enjoyed them all.  Cop Dog was a little sad, but the others had good adventure, sit on the edge of your seat, and good outcome, happy ending movies..

GREAT COLLECTION.  Bob Hope over a 20 year span of time, all Digitally Remastered. 1.  My Favorite Brunette (Hope/Lamore). 2. Road to Rio (Hope/Lamore/Crosby). 3. The Great Lover (Hope/Fleming/Reeves. 4. The Lemon Drop Kid (Hope/Maxwell/Frawley). 5. Son of Paleface (Hope/Russell/Roy Rogers). 6. Road to Bali (Hope/lamore/Crosby). 7. The Seven Little Foys (Hope/Cagney/Mathers). 8. Paris Holiday (Hope/Ekberg/Sturges). 9. The Private Navy of SGT. O'Farrell (Hope/Diller/Sargent). 10. How to Commit Marriage (Hope/Wyman/Gleason). What a wonderful collection with many hours of good, clean family humor and laughter. Enjoy.

Ohhh yes Cop Dog, it's just what every kid wants to see. It's filled with such great moments like visiting your dead fathers grave or watching your dog die. The dog isn't a cop, and it's barely a dog since it dies and spends most of the movie as a ghost.
Got these for my 7 year old grandson. I purchased them with 2 other collections and he was really excited when he realized he had 30 new movies.
My two grand daughters just loved this collection.  Highly recommend.
I thought all of the movies in this collection were great!
wonderful collection-good quality dvd.  delivered on time

I ordered this as a Christmas gift for some family members.  I put together a goody basket for them with sodas, popcorn, hot cocoa, candy, &, of course, these movies.  I thought they made a great gift (at a reasonable cost, too.)
